                'title' => 'Pet Memorials in Central Texas — Honoring Your Beloved Companion',
                'slug' => 'pet-memorials-central-texas',
                'body' => '<h2>Honoring a Beloved Pet with a Lasting Memorial</h2><p>Losing a pet is never easy. For many families, a beloved dog, cat, or companion animal is truly part of the family. The bond shared with a pet is filled with loyalty, comfort, and unconditional love, which is why more families today are choosing to honor their pets with a permanent memorial.</p><p>At Dietz Memorial, we have helped Central Texas families create custom pet memorial stones for years. Whether you want a simple garden marker or a fully personalized granite memorial, our team is here to help you create something meaningful and lasting.</p><h3>What Is a Pet Memorial Stone?</h3><p>A pet memorial stone is a custom granite marker designed to honor the life and memory of a beloved pet.</p><h3>Personalization Options</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Name and dates</strong> — Include your pet’s name along with birth and passing dates.</p></li><li><p><strong>Laser-etched portrait </strong>— Add a permanent engraved image of your pet using a favorite photograph.</p></li><li><p><strong>Custom message</strong> — Include a meaningful quote, short poem, or personal message.</p></li><li><p><strong>Paw prints or breed silhouettes </strong>— Decorative artwork can help personalize the design even further.</p></li><li><p><strong>Granite color choices </strong>— Select from a variety of natural granite colors and finishes.</p></li></ul><h3>Available Sizes</h3><ul><li><p><strong> Small garden stones </strong>— Ideal for cats and small dogs.</p></li><li><p><strong> Medium memorial markers </strong>— A popular option for most family pets.</p></li><li><p><strong>Full grave markers</strong> — Designed for pet cemeteries or larger memorial spaces.</p></li></ul><h3>Visit Dietz Memorial</h3><p>Visit our Waco or New Braunfels showroom locations to speak with our memorial specialists and create a meaningful tribute for your beloved companion.</p>',
                'excerpt' => 'Pets are family. When the time comes to say goodbye, a custom pet memorial stone is a beautiful way to honor the bond you shared. Here is what you need to know.',
